Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人有几台?还剩几台?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小林机严重损坏 山本机失去联络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精英侦察队全灭啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹夹空了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打光了最后一发子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是第几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还全是久经沙场的老兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长 你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是惊恐至极四处逃命时{\rsymbol}…{\r}被全歼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟{\rsymbol}…{\r}遭到了什么攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从残骸上看 应该是曳战者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是敌人的新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}青蓝和银色歼灭者 终有一天也会变成旧型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵器{\rsymbol}…{\r}完成设计开发 投入实战之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就已经过时了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长 莫非真的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持继续 慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔贝 希莫西亚 西坐摩原 肯尼文 以及北坐摩原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在这些附近重复攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵{\rsymbol}…{\r}吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铃城曹长 在士兵面前请别用这个称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人攻击的共通点 全都是歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有现场 都没有幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不想留下目击情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为应对这不明身份的敌人 我军铺开了复数部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎样 你们独立第八部队 既然被派到这北坐摩原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就表明作战指挥部很清楚这驻地的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又或者 敌人为实战测试新武器 选择了偏僻地区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局部的战术胜利 并不等于大局上战略胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强的一方获胜 差不多就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实大尉{\rsymbol}…{\r}多少有点权威主义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不必说那种话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部队执勤时间变更
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然说清楚比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心听了他姐姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 青蓝还有这机能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那{\rsymbol}…{\r}那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有邮件 传来了银色歼灭者控制插件的升级补丁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安{\rsymbol}…{\r}装前记得检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗯{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时候导入新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泽尔准将操持的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没法说不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机师的训练 兵站的处理 现场的负担都是问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撬动胶着战局 需要震撼疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负责开发的福达格伦特公司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说在各处塞了不少钞票 强揽了这笔活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该说的别说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们可被情报部盯着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知泽尔打得什么算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绕过情报部购入新型机 是想借我们个人情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就让他这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可别忘了 卡普
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论面对泽尔还是情报部 我们一定要装成傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这全是为了祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得饭菜如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃不如量足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种高档餐厅的饭菜 可填不饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因戈尔米亚的新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这人讨厌绕弯子 你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我们追加下单?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您明察 在下佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白你的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这玩意用了柯贝尔尼斯的技术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然一致罢了 而且技术本无国界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴还真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪件?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol2}「{\r}那件{\rsymbol2}」{\r}除了U-Link还能有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝无问题 请相信敝公司的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在萨卡拉岬角那时也是这句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨卡拉岬角?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为应对敌人新型曳战者攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 你们进入12小时两班轮换的迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚2000时起 至明早0800时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由进上等兵和波特曼上等兵值岗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥由先入队的进上等兵担当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0800时起 由阿普尔顿军曹和朱利亚诺伍长值岗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外 哈兹福特小姐 作为银色歼灭者运行辅助人员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请协助一同值夜岗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作战指挥部希望缴获敌机 但敌人性能未知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,视现场情况 允许当机立断将其击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波特曼小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才使劲求主厨 非要亲手做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol2}「{\r}诶{\rsymbol2}」{\r}什么 啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 就是有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开暖气了吗 你不觉得冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毯子啥的 应该随手就能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事? 插件我检查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个啥 最近状态挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联动深度也一直在涨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我这当负责人的 也觉得脸上有光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你咋了 看着这么别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}之前不小心听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗的{\rsymbol}…{\r}那个{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和左文字队长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是故意偷听的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧听见铃城小姐说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐和左文字队长{\rsymbol}…{\r}那个{\rsymbol}…{\r}关系亲密{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你姐姐去世时 他也在场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全听了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪最近 吉米都怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是隐私嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装不知道不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐因何而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军方咬定是事故 其他只字不提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 听铃城小姐讲完 终于知道了经过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说又觉得有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再怎么纠结 过去的也回不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那事儿都过了一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵{\rsymbol}…{\r}不出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没准已经成佛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能啊 净说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这么好对付 咱也不用费这劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就开个玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber-1呼叫Iron head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前 正与敌人交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请求火速支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron head 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber-1 与因戈尔米亚的曳战者交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber-1 这里是Iron head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回话 Saber-1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全军 进入位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通电左文字中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字中尉 接通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 你手下的新型机 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派到前面去 逐一告知状况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人消灭了巡视中的巡逻队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从方位一二五向总驻地移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲 劳伦斯的青蓝 已做好出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蓝-1 青蓝-2 将与银色歼灭者和青蓝-3汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然径直冲这边来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前线怎么样了 抓紧应对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不耍小伎俩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移动速度与银色歼灭者相当 甚至更高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新预计算接敌地点 发给机师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘木大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该把前线部队再铺开一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥由我负责 你提供情报就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与以往的因戈尔米亚机速度不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意 它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个混账{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠机 注意距离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘木大尉 请散开基地内曳战者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲 劳伦斯 向后撤确保地形优势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是新型机的威力?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:16:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲 劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗他们被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敌方炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦哟 这可麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中啊 打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联动深度 70
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,75
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报告状况 集中火力攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这混账{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠 受伤没?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部机体{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个问题怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止 没有明显征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:21:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉柯贝尔尼斯和福达格伦特 计划进入下一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在NR综合症显露之前 要不惜一切完成量产
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一点 命令两公司严格遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 里希特霍芬少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗德里克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准系统的延迟还没有改善
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要立刻调整
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是整备班说 现阶段这已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴风-A必须常保完美状态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就让他们改善
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于下一个作战目标{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变更
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到它了——银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}暴风
