Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:26.35,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:28.86,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:33.67,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:38.42,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:43.91,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:47.79,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:53.60,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:58.74,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:03.99,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:08.56,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:09.81,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:14.19,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:20.82,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.37,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:30.13,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.87,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.63,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.79,0:01:12.97,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 向着这无望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.97,0:01:17.59,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志将一飞冲天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.86,0:01:33.67,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是战友吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.93,0:01:38.42,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}当走之路是黑暗吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.02,0:01:43.91,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光闪动
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.06,0:01:47.79,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无名感情在胸中翻涌
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.98,0:01:53.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此时此刻在此地 尚不能结束-
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.60,0:01:58.74,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那么就做好活下去的准备吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.86,0:02:03.99,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔热忱 越积越高无处释放
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.99,0:02:08.56,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.94,0:02:14.19,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}战场之上 笑谈青涩有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.19,0:02:20.82,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我会一个一个亲自去实践
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.37,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放马过来{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:13.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見つめ合う  心  ひらいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:19.15,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}強がりと弱さのループ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:25.85,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ねえ少しは  慣れたはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:35.92,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉にしても全てのことは  わからないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:40.43,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}それだけは覚えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.64,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}こんなものじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:46.98,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}自分に気付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:54.18,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}勇気に乗せたなら  世界は変わっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:23:01.95,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}独りじゃ知らなかった  あのTELEPATHY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:08.42,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}導く  後ろ姿  とても眩しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:15.45,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}だから私は  目をそらさず君を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:22.37,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}届くと  信じている
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.04,0:22:13.20,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}对视凝望  将心扉敞开
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.60,0:22:19.15,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}逞强与软弱的循环
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.49,0:22:25.85,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}呐  是不是  略微习惯了些
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.27,0:22:35.92,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}即便用语言阐述  也不是一切事情  都能清晰明了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.38,0:22:40.43,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我只记住了这个道理
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.64,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}并不是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.98,0:22:46.98,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}自己去发现
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.35,0:22:54.18,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}只要拿出勇气前行  世界会随之改变
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.78,0:23:01.95,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}独自一人绝不可能注意到  那TELEPATHY
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.61,0:23:08.42,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}引领我的那个背影  如此光辉耀眼
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.64,0:23:15.45,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}所以我目不转睛  一直注视着你
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.07,0:23:22.37,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}相信你会懂我的心
